DURATION:4 WEEKS

OVERVIEW OF THE PROJECT
![Screenshot (6)](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/269bda34-f6a6-4597-b6eb-483ed880983d)

PROJECT:BUILD A PROGRAM THAT GENERATES A RANDOM NUMBER AND CHALLENGES THE USER TO GUESS IT.THE PROGRAM SHOULD PROMPT THE USER TO INPUT THEIR
GUESS,COMPARE IT TO THE GENERTED NUMBER

OBJECTIVES
Random Number Generation:

Implement a method to generate a random number within a specified range.

User Interaction:

Prompt the user to input their guess and provide feedback on whether the guess is too high, too low, or correct.

Comparison Logic:

Compare the user's guess to the randomly generated number and determine the result of each guess.

Feedback and Hints:

Provide the user with hints to guide their next guess, enhancing the interactive experience.

Loop Until Correct:

Allow the user to continue guessing until they correctly identify the generated number.

Scorekeeping and Attempts:

Track the number of attempts the user takes to guess the correct number and display it at the end of the game.

User-Friendly Interface:

Ensure the program is easy to use and understand, providing clear instructions and feedback throughout.

Replayability:

Offer an option to play again after successfully guessing the number, encouraging repeated engagement.
